sequenceDiagram
    participant User
    participant CM as Conversation Manager
    participant Router as Intent Router
    participant LLM as LLM Provider
    
    User->>CM: "Find expensive queries in job 123"
    
    Note over CM: Step 1: Receive user message
    
    CM->>Router: classify_intent(message, history)
    
    Note over Router: Step 2: Analyze request
    
    Router->>Router: Pattern matching<br/>(keywords, regex)
    
    alt Pattern match found
        Router-->>CM: Direct route to agent
    else Need LLM classification
        Router->>LLM: "Classify this request:<br/>User: 'Find expensive queries in job 123'<br/>Available domains: query, job, uc, analytics..."
        
        Note over LLM: Analyzes intent using<br/>domain knowledge
        
        LLM-->>Router: {<br/>  "primary": "job",<br/>  "secondary": ["query"],<br/>  "confidence": 0.95<br/>}
        
        Router->>Router: Select primary agent<br/>(JobAgent)
        
        Router-->>CM: Route to JobAgent<br/>with secondary hints
    end
    
    Note over CM: Step 3: Create appropriate agent
    
    CM->>CM: create_agent(JobAgent)
    
    CM-->>User: Processing with JobAgent...
    
    Note over User: Routing complete<br/>Agent selected based on intent

